FBIS4-36571 "drnes112_j_94004" FBIS-NES-94-112 Daily Report 9 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Aden Reports Northern Forces Resuming Attacks Aden Reports Northern Forces Resuming Attacks EA0906170294 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in Arabic 1500 GMT 9 Jun 94 EA0906170294 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in Arabic 1500 GMT 9 Jun 94 Arabic BFN [Excerpt] A responsible source at the Democratic Republic of Yemen [DRY] Defense Ministry has issued the following statement to the YEMENI NEWS AGENCY, Aden: The forces of the ruling military regime in Sanaa at dawn today resumed their iniquitous, aggressive operations against our people in the DRY on all fronts, continuing their random shelling of populated residential areas and vital economic installations, in implementation of orders issued by war general 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih, who yesterday ordered his forces to continue their destruction, regardless of the cost. [passage omitted]
